imeline-topic\">Stochastic Calculus</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Optimization Theory</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-entry\">\n<div class=\"vtimeline-dot w3\"></div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-header\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-week w3\">W3</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-title\">C++ Low-Latency Patterns</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-phase\">Phase 3</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-topics\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Lock-Free Queues</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Wait-Free Hazard Pointers</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Memory Pool Allocators</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Atomic Operations</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Cache-Friendly Data Structures</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Placement New</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">SIMD Intrinsics</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-entry\">\n<div class=\"vtimeline-dot w4\"></div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-header\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-week w4\">W4</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-title\">System Programming & IPC</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-phase\">Phase 4</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-topics\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Shared Memory</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">FlatBuffers</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">SBE</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Binary Logging</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Binary Size Optimization</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Build Systems</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Cross Compilation</span>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-entry\">\n<div class=\"vtimeline-dot w5\"></div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-header\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-week w5\">W5</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-title\">Kernel Bypass & Protocols</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-phase\">Phase 5</span>\n</div>\n<div class=\"vtimeline-topics\">\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">Kernel Bypass (DPDK/Onload)</span>\n<span class=\"vtimeline-topic\">FIX Protocol</span>